set view.characters.hobo.image = 'buttstacks'
set view.characters.hobo.name = 'Boris J. Buttstacks'

Hobo [worried]: Allo there... where d'ya think you're goin'? Just waltzin' into town? You ain't gettin' through unless I say so.
go menu-kittens

# menu-kittens
Arca:
	- Who are you? -> who
	- (unless asked-passage) I don't have much time - can't you just let me pass? -> passage
	- (unless asked-kittens) I'm here to look for missing kittens - have you heard anything? -> kittens
	- (unless asked-clothes) Why are your clothes so dirty? -> clothes

# passage
set asked-passage
Hobo [irritated]: Nah-ah. This is my town. I'm th'mayor. Completely legit. Dy'a get it? I rule it here. And it ain't the first kid want'in to visit that can get in just like that.
go menu-kittens

# kittens
set asked-kittens
Hobo [worried]: Strange ya mentioned that. A funny lookin' chap with a tail came an' asked where he could find kittens, just t'other day. Didn't like the look of his jumper, so I told 'im to bob off.
Arca:
	- Oh... did he say why he was looking for them?
		continue
	- Did you get his name?
		continue
	- Do you know where he was going?
		continue
		
Hobo [irritated]: Nup, he didn't say.
go menu-kittens

# clothes
set asked-clothes
Hobo [irritated]: What the Newt kinda question is that? No offense kid, but that's rich coming from someone dressed as a turnip.
Arca:
	- It's a cape... capes are awesome!
		Hobo [irritated]: Hmph! Who do you think you are? Wonder Walrus?

	- These are the only clothes I have.
		Hobo [smug]: Don't be lazy, there are lots of bins around 'ere. Tha's where I get all my clothes.

	- What's so bad about looking like a turnip? 
	  Hobo [irritated]: Hmmm. I've avoided turnips ever since the accident...
go menu-kittens

# who
set asked-who
branch:
	- (if asked-passage) Hobo [smug]: I'm Boris J. Buttstacks - the town's mayor, as I might 'ave mentioned. As in, I rule th'whole town. As mayors do. And I'm the mayor, fo'real. I'm legit.
	- (default) Hobo [smug]: I'm Boris J. Buttstacks - the town's mayor. As in, I rule th'whole town. As mayors do. And I'm the mayor, fo'real. I'm legit.
go menu-mission

# menu-mission
Arca:
	- What do I need to do, to pass through? -> mission
	- (unless asked-why) Okay, okay - so you're the mayor. Why can't you let me pass? -> why
	- (unless asked-how) How did you get to be mayor? -> how
		
# why
set asked-why
Hobo [smug]: You scratch my feet, I'll scratch yours. That's 'ow the world works, y'know.
go menu-mission

# how
set asked-how
Hobo [irritated]: Hmph! How rude! I'm the mayor, and that's that.
go menu-mission

# mission
set asked-mission
Hobo[neutral]: Well... Ya gonna need to go and fetch some stuff for me. Imma give you some addresses that will help ya find my stuff. Got it?
go menu-onions

# menu-onions
Arca:
	- Okay. What do you need me to fetch? -> onions
	- (unless asked-time) I need to rescue the missing kittens - I really don't have much time -> time

# onions
set asked-onions
Hobo [neutral]: Well see, I'm a big fan o' pickled onions. Could eat a thousand an' beg fo'more. Ya gonna need to go to Bulbous Island and get me a big'ol'jar of pickled onions, if ya please. I've written down the address for ya.
go menu-lets-go

# time
set asked-time
Hobo [really-happy]: Nice work spud! Ya found the perfect place for me an' Dusty.
go menu

# menu
Arca:
	- Er...can I go now? -> go
	- (unless asked-explore) Good luck on your date! -> good-luck
	- (unless asked-romantic) I'm sure it'll be very romantic. -> romantic

# romantic
set asked-romantic
Hobo [lovestruck]: Dusty and meee, sitting in a tree, K.I.S.S.I.N.G. Oh Dusty, I love you!
go menu

# good-luck
set asked-go
Hobo [really-happy]: Thanks spud! Ain't been this excited since the Great Candy Floss Tornado of 1993. Have y'ever tried flyin' and eatin' at the same time? Ain't nothin' like it.
go menu

# go
set asked-go
Hobo [irritated]: Yes, but you'll have to wait till I get back. Can't be late for my date!
go finish

Hobo [irritated]: Well then, you best be quick.
go menu-onions

# menu-lets-go
Arca: 
	- Fine, I'll go and get your onions -> finish
	- Yuk. I'll try and be quick. -> finish
